query:
SELECT 
  'Teachers for Council Chat' as feature,
  COUNT(*) as available_count
FROM teachers
WHERE fullName IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Embeddings for RAG',
  COUNT(*)
FROM embeddings
WHERE embedding IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Key Ideas for Context',
  COUNT(*)
FROM keyIdeas
WHERE teacherId IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Practices for Recommendations',
  COUNT(*)
FROM practices
WHERE teacherId IS NOT NULL;
